                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10043" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0297</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">457 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">积羽成舟，破茧成蝶——华丰科技的混改上市之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Accumulating feathers into a boat, breaking cocoons into butterflies: Huafeng Technology&#39;s mixed ownership reform and listing path</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杨进，张文丽，魏千朋，杨超</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西南科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">四川华丰科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国企混改；员工持股；公司治理；股份制改革</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">State owned enterprise mixed ownership reform, employee shareholding, corporate governance, and shareholding system reform</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">四川华丰科技有限公司曾面临连续亏损与发展停滞的困境。为破局求生，公司系统性地推进了混合所有制改革。通过存续分立有效剥离了历史包袱，实现了轻装上阵；引入员工持股，激励团队并稳定了核心人才；引入战略投资者，不仅增强了资本实力，也优化了股权结构与公司治理。华丰混改成效显著，公司盈利能力发生根本性扭转。以2022年为例，公司实现营业收入9.84亿元，净利润达9309万元，与混改前夕年亏损9674万元形成鲜明对比。此后，公司成功登陆上海证券交易所科创板，上市后市值一度突破100亿元，充分体现了市场对其改革成果与发展前景的高度认可。华丰的案例生动揭示了国有企业通过混改激发内生动力、提升市场竞争力的可行路径，华丰的成功经验为面临类似困境的传统企业提供了一套可借鉴的系统性改革方法论。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Sichuan Huafeng Technology Co., Ltd. once faced the challenges of continuous losses and stagnant development. To break the deadlock and ensure survival, the company systematically advanced mixed-ownership reform. Through a surviving spin-off, it effectively shed historical burdens, achieving unburdened development. The introduction of employee stock ownership incentivized the team and stabilized core talent. The inclusion of strategic investors not only strengthened capital capacity but also optimized the equity structure and corporate governance.The mixed-ownership reform at Huafeng yielded remarkable results, fundamentally reversing the company’s profitability. In 2022, for instance, the company achieved an annual revenue of 984 million yuan, with a net profit of 93.09 million yuan, a stark contrast to the annual loss of 96.74 million yuan on the eve of the reform. Subsequently, the company successfully listed on the Shanghai Stock Exchange’s Sci-Tech Innovation Board, with its market capitalization once exceeding 10 billion yuan, fully reflecting the market’s high recognition of its reform achievements and development prospects. Huafeng’s case vividly demonstrates how state-owned enterprises can stimulate endogenous drivers and enhance market competitiveness through mixed-ownership reform. Its successful experience provides a replicable and systematic reform methodology for traditional enterprises facing similar challenges.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">委托-代理理论；制度刚性理论；资源依赖理论；激励相容理论；路径依赖理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-11</td>
